23.000Z","msg":"同屆同學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔熟<br />\n但琴晚都即時諗起佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1047d3cfb23d11e5893c125e13741d428ed18b0a","tid":1229962,"uid":42586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T05:44:37.000Z","msg":"never forget never forgive"},{"pid":"e7fcee7e139ebd5f16adc7744e967dea6f708c32","tid":1229962,"uid":72009,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T05:46:30.000Z","msg":"走得太前，死了大家仲吃喝玩樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1329e0577e22c8f056c395ad5d4747c98a45e4e","tid":1229962,"uid":229275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T05:47:39.000Z","msg":"我尋晚都有諗起佢<br />\n可惜我地都阻止唔到"}]}